## Why use React Native : ğŸ“Œ 

    ğŸ”¥ Cross Platform:
        ğŸ”° One of the most important advantage of React Native is that you can develop application for both Android and IOS ecosystem simultaneously by writing the same code.

    ğŸ”¥ No need to learn Platform Specific languages :
        ğŸ”° One does not need to learn languages for specific platforms to develop application ; like we don't need to learn kotlin for developing apps for Android environment or Swift  for IOS environment. React Native only uses JavaScript , the most popular programming language .

    ğŸ”¥ Large Developer Communities :
        ğŸ”° React Native has a large developer communities which ensures speedy query solving and also adequate support is available for react native developers.

    ğŸ”¥ Better Career Opportunities :
        ğŸ”° Due to advantages like cross-platform compatibility , React Native Developers have high demand.


 ##     React Native Apps    Vs   Platform - Specific Apps : ğŸ“Œ 

    ğŸ”¶ React Native Apps : 
            ğŸ“ App works in both IOS and Android
            ğŸ“ Build time is Fast.
            ğŸ“Applications are simple.
            ğŸ“ Developers have strong web development background.
    
    ğŸ”¶ Platform Specific Apps :
            ğŸ“ App is made for specific platform.
            ğŸ“ Build time is slow.
            ğŸ“Applications are complex.
            ğŸ“Developers have strong platform knowledge.
            

